],"id":"24699ab8-3cca-252a-f375-8762ed67f7cb","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Check Calendar Availability\n\ngoogleCalendar — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Slot Free? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"576b794c-b009-2d2c-fc10-389903ff5f0f","name":"Note: Check Calendar Availability"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Slot Free?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $items().length === 0 || !$json.id }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Create Calendar Event · ②→ Propose Alternative Slots","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"eed14028-7bbe-7d41-e1d8-5e10650e96c1","name":"Note: Slot Free?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Create Calendar Event\n\ngoogleCalendar — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,280],"id":"f596ac41-0058-89a9-d6d6-be832ac61089","name":"Note: Create Calendar Event"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams)\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hold Until Reminder Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"5d1a72b6-dea4-f4b6-6974-bc24b606cc7c","name":"Note: Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Propose Alternative Slots\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"49365530-f6e4-c1fd-b428-49b435e8e0f2","name":"Note: Propose Alternative Slots"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Until Reminder Time\n\nPauses 1 hours — spacing calls to respect rate limits.\n\nNext: Send Reminder (Microsoft Teams)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"92fe4b85-14c7-5953-ef9a-3263a410aaa6","name":"Note: Hold Until Reminder Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Reminder (Microsoft Teams)\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"bcd5f7ff-b0e4-a25b-ab6b-a0a6d687476d","name":"Note: Send Reminder (Microsoft Teams)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"4f6e8530-5ebe-a512-3d42-fe7fe6aa1860","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"1d1f3064-67c5-0232-749d-eca1eeb44d03","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"a9ad5e8a-1e59-aa15-1671-9d58d048eb9c","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Book demos with Google Calendar and Microsoft Teams 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Meeting Scheduling · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nBook demos with Google Calendar and Microsoft Teams 24/7. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual calendar sync is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Booking Form Submission → Stamp & Shape Booking → Payload Valid? → Check Calendar Availability → Slot Free? → Create Calendar Event → Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams) → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to meeting scheduling without manual effort\n- Anyone automating calendar sync in healthcare\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"3ca82338-f02a-cc88-18e8-dd08c7ebc0db","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"35f30c8d-1c17-52f6-c35c-998568c07ba4","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"c612571b-32b8-b1ca-867f-b9c31550f7d0","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your calendar sync process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"e98f755c-23f3-2a87-f9fb-625b17a3bba9","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Booking Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Booking","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Booking":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Check Calendar Availability","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Check Calendar Availability":{"main":[[{"node":"Slot Free?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Slot Free?":{"main":[[{"node":"Create Calendar Event","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Propose Alternative Slots","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Create Calendar Event":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Confirmation (Microsoft Teams)":{"main":[[{"node":"Hold Until Reminder Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold Until Reminder Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Reminder (Microsoft Teams)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Reminder (Microsoft Teams)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Propose Alternative Slots":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"ac2e8a13-838c-4d23-8b57-0739899cb240","id":"FDX09843"}